C-932 September Term 2017
080881 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 15, 2018

In the MATTER OF the APPLICATION FOR the EXPUNGEMENT OF the CRIMINAL RECORD BELONGING TO J.W.

(J.W.-Petitioner)

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001730-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
